name: Fauna Flowers 05 - Arara Flower
description:
Take yourself a time to admire this rare blue one. Just a few of this species remain on our planet. If you fall in love with it, lucky you, cause it pairs for life.
A great confidant whose chatter can provide good times. It teaches us how to be mindful of what we say. Its vital talking to it and petting it daily.
A unique symbol of hope and beauty.

Fauna Flowers is a collection made of animals mixed with plants in a new kind of magical possibilities. Discover this world where flowers can be a magnificent diversity of beautiful and unique creatures.
